Package aProject

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CreateDB
    The CreateDB class stores the methods on how to connect to MySQL, create the aProjectDB database, create the caseLocations and login tables, and populate the login table with login data for three users for Group #2's term group programming project.
    DataPoint
    The DataPoint class stores data about an accident (case) represented by a data point for Group #2's term group programming project.
    DataPointSet
    This class represents a collection of DataPoints and the associated userlevel of the user.
    Login
    The Login class stores data associated with the user's authentication credentials (username, password, and user type level).
    MIS_Project
    This class is the main class for the "Pedestrian and Bicyclist Safety Tool" The program provides end users with an interactive tool for crash data point mapping.
    Point
    The Point class stores geographical marker data (latitude, longitude, and elevation) about an accident (point) for Group #2's term group programming project.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CaseType
    This enum lists all of the possible (accident) case types.
    UserLevelType
    This enum lists all of the possible UserLevelType values.
